Automatically downloads Zabbix and created DEB package for the platform where this script is being run. 

Debian, probably Ubuntu. Tested with Debian 6 (squeeze). 

git clone https://github.com/hecko/zabbix-agent-debian.git
cd zabbix-agent-debian
./build.sh

does not automatically install rc script(s)

does not automatically create zabix user

zabbix-server is a default hostname for zabbix server in the agent config - so change your /etc/hosts accordingly
